collectible.name: 1st Air Faction Flying Motorcycle and Mining Machine - Scarcity
collectible.description: This is the first vehicle produced by the Air Faction, specifically by Crisa. You can use it to fly between the islands of the metaverse in comfort and safety, and you can also use it as a land mining machine capable of drilling through the toughest structures. After the war, almost all of them were destroyed, and now they are very rare: just 8 remained.
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b

collectible.name: The Metaverse Architects' Clipboard
collectible.description:
The Metaverse Architects' Clipboard: Used to hold down field notes, sketches, blue prints... sometimes you just need a flat spot to sign the guest book! A must-have for any metaverse creator.

Post-mint update: Works very well in the "forearm" spot

collectible.name: Not to the Eye Entrance Poster - Anti-Eye Citizens
collectible.description: The Eye is a physical structure, made by Hallo, where all Anons can upload their experiences and watch all the experiences uploaded in the system. The Anti-Eye citizens say that it is a brainwashing experience, and that it is artificial and do not make us close to humanity. This is a poster from an Anti-Eye meeting.
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b
